match between two players at a basketball game in Detroit. Bush's
lawyer, Otis Underwood, argued that a fall might have killed Dudley.
   Harding was convicted Thursday of felony murder. Bush was
convicted Wednesday of first-degree murder. They are both already
serving prison sentences for the robbery and assault.
